==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ingirt
<hw>In*girt"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Ingirt</er>.]</ety> <def>To encircle; to gird; to engirt.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The wreath is ivy that <qex>ingirts</qex> our beams.</q>
<rj><qau>Drayton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ingirt</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ingirt
<hw>In*girt"</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Surrounded; encircled.</def>
<rj><au>Fenton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ingle</ent>⟦br⟧
